<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/style.css" />
    <title>TCC</title>
  </head>
  <style>
    * {
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      background-image: linear-gradient(
        to right top,
        #051937,
        #004d7a,
        #008793,
        #032e52,
        #a8eb12
      );
      background-color: #ff3cac;
      background-image: linear-gradient(
        to right top,
        #004d7a 0%,
        #784ba0 50%,
        #2b86c5 100%
      );
    }

    .container {
      width: 80%;
      height: 80vh;
      display: flex;
      box-shadow: 5px 5px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.212);
    }

    .form-image {
      width: 50%;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      background-color: #fde3a7d7;
      padding: 1rem;
    }

    .form-image img {
      width: 31rem;
    }

    .form {
      width: 50%;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      background-color: rgba(240, 228, 228, 0.842);
      padding: 3rem;
    }

    .form-header {
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      width: 100%;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .out-button {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .out-button button {
      border: none;
      background-color: #16a085;
      padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 5px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .out-button button:hover {
      background-color: #16a085;
    }

    .out-button button a {
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .form-header h1::after {
      content: "";
      display: block;
      width: 5rem;
      height: 0.3rem;
      background-color: #16a085;
      margin: 0 auto;
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    .continue-button button {
      width: 100%;
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
      border: none;
      background-color: #16a085;
      padding: 0.62rem;
      border-radius: 5px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .input-group {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 1rem 0;
    }

    .continue-button button:hover {
      background-color: #16a084d7;
    }

    .continue-button button a {
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.93rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #fff;
    }

    @media screen and (max-width: 1330px) {
      .form-image {
        display: none;
      }

      .container {
        width: 50%;
      }

      .form {
        width: 100%;
      }
    }

    @media screen and (max-width: 1064px) {
      .container {
        width: 90%;
        height: auto;
      }

      .form-header {
        width: 100%;
      }

      .input-group {
        flex-direction: column;
        z-index: 5;
        padding-right: 5rem;
        max-height: 10rem;
        overflow-y: scroll;
        flex-wrap: nowrap;
      }
    }
  </style>

  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="form-image">
        <iframe src="https://giphy.com/embed/eNMrFVCX3KQO5vNVaM"> </iframe>
      </div>
      <div class="form">
        <form action="#">
          <div class="form-header">
            <div class="title">
              <h1>Sobre nós</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="out-button">
              <button><a href="/principal">Voltar</a></button>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="input-group">
            <h3>Olá, tudo bem? Espero que sim =D</h3>
            <p>
              Estamos aqui para apresentar a vocês o grande <b>Talento</b> que
              adquirimos ao longo do curso. Habilidades que jamais serão
              disperdiçadas enquanto andarmos nessa Terra.
            </p>
            <p>
              Giovanni Trintinalia e Renan Soares cumpriram sua missão em
              oferecer um sistema capaz de realizar a análise de reconhecimento
              de imagem utilizando <b>AWS Rekognition</b>. O mundo é um lugar
              melhor agora e as pessoas podem reconhecer seus produtos em paz
              absoluta e viver em harmonia.
            </p>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
